cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with image processing and restoration using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of a pyramidal CNN architecture and the collection of a large-scale dataset suggest that the paper may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories.
